# Code Reuse

Follow `rules/code-reuse.md`:

1. Search codebase before adding new code.
2. Validators -> `packages/shared/validators/` (single Zod schema for web + API).
3. API calls -> `apps/web/src/lib/api-client.ts` only.
4. Constants/enums -> `packages/shared/constants/`.
5. If same logic appears twice, extract before continuing.

Never copy-paste validators, DTOs, or formatters between apps.
